reviews.text: Excellent massage for ladies as well gents. Loved it.

Pretty good option as there aren't many alternatives out there. I went on a weekday and it was pretty quiet. The ladies facility doesn't not look very new, but it's acceptable. Base on conversation with my boyfriend, the mens' experience seems to be better - they have a hot bath and cold bath, which the ladies don't have. Apparently they have a chinese herbal scented steam room, but the ladies' is just lemons. After comparing our experiences I feel duped.
It's nice to have a sauna once in a while, but the overall experience/ value won't bring me back for pleasure, only for necessity.
Not much Sauna left in Hong Kong, well, can't take photo but I met Joe Junior the singer there
Best schvitz in the East! Old school HK vibes. Great medicinal herbs steam room!
Great service.  Great value. I will likely do it a again.
